{"tid":2057614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安倍指現時非協調習近平訪日時機 平息疫情最重要","createTime":"2020-06-09T13:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T13:56:49.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d836e3787a225b051e4ff86aa7373b77abf2efc7","tid":2057614,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:50:43.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平國事訪問日本受新型肺炎疫情一再延後。日本首相安倍晉三認為，現階段平息疫情比甚麼都重要，至少現時並非協調習近平具體訪日日程的時候。<br />\n<br />\n安倍日前在國會說，正觀察香港局勢，對於北京就香港進行國家安全立法，深感憂慮。他形容香港在經濟聯繫及人文交流層面，都是日本極為重要的合作夥伴，香港能夠維持「一國兩制」，以穩定及民主方式處理事情，非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531059-20200609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531059-20200609.htm&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=8731973d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531059-20200609.htm&h=95a99142\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531059-20200609.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a5d65e00554e92429397e74da526fe6d2d4e01e3","tid":2057614,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"近期絕對係要開戰<br />\n美國印度日本同盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">[&darr;&darr;港獨強心針&darr;&darr;]<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港最強力盟友USA : <br />\n國際反共 形勢大好<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcopPX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcopPX</a></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"6ce5b84b22e0ea2a2b9950d1bafba784ee6422bb","tid":2057614,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"c<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}